Usage: specifySpareGate [-help] {-cell <cellName> | -inst <instName> | -hinst <hinstName>}

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cellName>     # cell name (wild card) to be specified as spare cells
                     # (string, optional)
-hinst <hinstName>   # hinst name (wild card) to be specified as spare cell
                     # (string, optional)
-inst <instName>     # inst name (wild card) to be specified as spare cell
                     # (string, optional)